title: Frictions over investigations emerge after ICE agent fatally shoots Minneapolis woman
description: Minnesota officials launch their own effort to collect evidence in the killing of Renee Good by an ICE agent. The move comes after shootings involving federal agents in Minneapolis and Portland, Ore.
